oai_dc:dc.dc:title: 528 North 2nd Street, 1959
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the house at 528 North 2nd Street, 9 December 1959. The house was located within the boundaries of the East Nashville Urban Renewal Area. Photographed by Jerry Hiland of the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
